Excellent insult, Minime! Qwest customer servive employee would also be good. 
I have been having urges to call and cuss them out. Just for fun.

::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Zardus frowns, looking at Voluis as the bot also flies off.

"Slapped?" he replies to Battera, "By whom?"

He had a feeling he knew the answer. Zardus lands near DevilDuer. "Follow 
that bot. See what he's doing."

DevilDuer nods, transforming into beast mode and running into the forest, 
making no noise as he follows after Voluis.
